# migration

Database migration files for `{{ .Name }}`.

Recommended tools: `goose` or `golang-migrate`. Name files with a sequential numeric prefix so they run in order:

```
0001_create_users.sql
0002_add_email_index.sql
0003_add_roles_table.sql
```

Run migrations with `make migrate-up` (add the target to `Makefile` once you pick a tool).
